properties.areaDesc: Santa Catalina and Rincon Mountains including Mount Lemmon/Summerhaven
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 2 at 12:42PM MST until February 3 at 7:00PM MST by NWS Tucson AZ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest to west winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts mainly to
60 mph expected.

* WHERE...Catalina and Rincon Mountains.

* WHEN...From 10 AM to 7 PM MST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM TO 7 PM MST MONDAY
